As an AI, I don't have access to any personal information about you, so I don't know your name.

You would need to tell me if you'd like me to know it for our conversation!

Okay, Sachin! It's nice to meet you.

I'll remember that your name is Sachin for our conversation. How can I help you today, Sachin?
give me all the info you have about me?

Okay, Sachin.

The only piece of information I have about you is what you've told me in this current conversation: **that your name is Sachin.**

As an AI, I don't have access to any personal data about you, your past interactions, or any external information. My memory is limited to our current conversation, and I don't store details about you across different sessions.
